tspan.tspan: - veh_id: ID of the vehicle this controller is used for
- delay: delay in applying the action (time)
- display_warnings: flag for toggling on/off printing failsafe warnings to screen
- noise: variance of the gaussian from which to sample a noisy acceleration
- T: safe time headway, in s (default: 1)
- s0: linear jam distance, in m (default: 2)
_ k_v: gain on the difference between lead velocity and
- k_c: gain on the difference from the desired velocity to
- tau: lag time between control input u and real
- alpha: gain on the desired velocity to the current
- beta: gain on lead car velocity and self-velocity
- wanted_max_accel: whether to reach the max
